    - target: {fileID: 5596622687143516412, guid: e5b3fe4d53d02be4e8bb8a09f2825dca, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '



        WE HAVE DECIDED TO LEAVE!


        There is no reason
        for the military to be out here anymore.

        If You''re wondering why
        we are leaving all this equipment behind, well they dont work anymore. For
        some reason they all went silent a couple days back gods know why.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
